id: pm-vvib
title: "ADR: cognitive memory architecture — agent context assembly modeled on human memory systems (proposed)"
description: "Unifying design decision for the context engine: working/episodic/semantic/procedural memory, consolidation, associative recall, and graceful forgetting each map to a named pm primitive. Dedupe-checked: no existing cognitive/memory-architecture decision item."
type: Decision
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: adr,"area:sdk",context-management
created_at: "2026-07-06T23:46:02.648Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-07T14:44:15.568Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: "ADR reviewed and moved to accepted or rejected with rationale recorded; if accepted: the mapping table names one owning implementation item per memory subsystem, pm-atfm scenario classes include returning-agent continuity cases, and a docs context-architecture page task is filed"
parent: pm-m2u1
risk: low
confidence: medium
